      "remarks": "DoD CC SRG Impact Level 5 (IL5) National Security System (NSS) baseline. Reconciled directly from the official Rev 5 SSP Addendum spreadsheet, sheet ' IL5 (NSS)' (578 NIST 800-53 Rev 5 controls; 0 additional GRR-* General Readiness Requirements rows are non-NIST and excluded). Structure: (1) Import the NIST 800-53 Rev 5 HIGH baseline and include the 362 controls flagged 'Leveraged from FedRAMP High = Yes' that appear in NIST HIGH; (2) explicitly exclude 0 HIGH controls not present in the IL5 (NSS) sheet; (3) import the full Rev 5 catalog to add 38 FedRAMP-High-only controls (PT family, IR-9.x, etc.) and 178 NSS overlay additions (the canonical ~178 net-new IL5 NSS controls per CC SRG v1r4); (4) apply DoD-Specified Parameter Values (DSPAV) for 21 parameters. Cross-check against the current SRG release before use in any authorization package."
    },
